    "## The \"Best\" neighborhood\n",
    "\n",
    "Based on our combined data analysis, the best neighborhood is **New Homestead**.\n",
    "This neighborhood achieved the highest overall score by performing consistently well across all three metrics: low crime rates, strong housing conditions, and high employment levels.\n",
    "Its balanced performance across these categories makes it the top-ranked neighborhood according to our data-driven model."
